           SHORT="KDE Twin-Panel filemanager ala commander style"

cat << EOF
Krusader is an "old-school" file manager. Its twin-panel look follows in the
footsteps of the great file managers of old such as GNU's Midnight Commander(c)
and the Norton Commander(c) for DOS. Krusader features an intuitive GUI,
complete drag n' drop capability, transparent handling of archives, mimetype
support, and more.
EOF
